

First setup virtual environment to install all dependencies for project.
activate virtual environment
run command pip -r requirements.txt to install all dependencies.

Setup database using python manage.py makemigration and python manage.py migrate
Start server using python manage.py runserver

Endpoints

User Signup
URL: /api/signup/
Method: POST
Data: json ( user data)

Generate OTP
URL: /api/gen-otp/
Method: POST
Data: json (username)

User Login
URL: /api/login/
Method: POST
Data: json (username, otp)

Update Full Name
URL: /api/update-fullname/
Method: POST
Data: json ( new full name along with authorization header)


